   "Survival only bought them a date with each other. The bracket now sends Pilsner and El Farolito straight into a losers'-bracket collision \u2014 win or go home \u2014 which means one of the two best teams left standing behind Rawhides will be gone in the very next round. Four seasons of pedigree on one side, the field's hottest form team on the other, and a single ticket out.",
   "The glass slipper still fits. Route 101, the 12th seed that has spent this tournament stealing games it has no business winning, did it again \u2014 a 9-8 escape over Lucky Horseshoe. Every game it has won has come down to the final rack \u2014 both of its victories 9-8. The Dalmatians have next to no title equity, but they refuse to lose the close ones, and they are somehow still dancing.",
